dct_description_sm: Some sights are shown pictorially. Inset map of Tokyo Bay; sightseeing bus tour information, and black and white photographs on recto. On verso: Map of Subways -- Map of Ginza, Nihombashi and Marunouchi area. Includes index and bus pick up service schedule listed by hotel names.
